{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to laugh because when-- when my uncle told me after the war what was in this carriage, that was a great source of pride to me because I was running around telling my friends that I was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though I didn't know anything what was in this carriage, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But hey, I contributed in some way to the war effort.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was-- that was very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was important that as many people know as possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Another incident that I remember was, one winter when most of the people in our hut were sick with typhus.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if I had it too, or I didn't have it, or if I had it, I had it in a milder form.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have such a high fever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went out to chop some wood, which, again, some of Babushka's friends had brought to the hut, but it was lying outside in the snow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also outside there, there was this big-- to me it looked like a giant, rusty ax.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I could hardly pick it up and I needed to chop this wood to bring it to warm up in the hut, to make people feel a little better.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, most of them were delirious and they didn't know what's going on with themselves anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was trying to chop this wood because this was the thing to do, because I wanted to help.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course I-- I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- the ax fell on my finger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my finger started bleeding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I started-- I just stood there frozen and I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And out of nowhere, this Romanian soldier appeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
